      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "but it's not just about \"change\" or \"moving forward.\" it feels more permanent than that. like the actual spark, the thing that made me *me*, is just gone. i'm just going through the motions, eating, sleeping, working... but there's nothing behind my eyes anymore. it feels like i'm just waiting for the rest of me to catch up to the part that already died.",
      "beast_suffix": "",
      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
